---
// Guided walkthrough demo of the consult builder for the How-it-works section.
// The markup ships in the finished "review" state so the no-JS, reduced-motion,
// and crawler floors always show a complete note; how-demo.ts rewinds and plays
// the phases only when it is actually going to animate.
---

<div
    class="how-demo"
    id="how-demo"
    data-phase="review"
    role="img"
    aria-label="Demonstration of Consultologist turning a pasted referral into a consultation note section by section, with a visible progress trail"
>
    <div class="demo-inner" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="demo-card demo-draft">
            <span class="demo-label">Consult draft</span>
            <p class="demo-draft-text">
                Thank you for seeing this 58-year-old with six weeks of symmetric small-joint
                pain and morning stiffness. RF and anti-CCP positive. Please assess and advise
                on management…
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="demo-card demo-note">
            <div class="demo-note-header">
                <span class="demo-note-title">Consultation note</span>
                <span class="demo-badge">3 sections</span>
            </div>
            <div class="demo-body">
                <div class="demo-placeholder">
                    <span></span>
                    <span></span>
                    <span></span>
                </div>
                <div class="demo-section is-visible" data-section="hpi">
                    <h4>History of Present Illness</h4>
                    <p>
                        Six weeks of symmetric polyarthralgia involving the MCPs and wrists,
                        with morning stiffness lasting more than an hour and partial response
                        to NSAIDs.<span class="demo-caret"></span>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="demo-section is-visible" data-section="impression">
                    <h4>Impression</h4>
                    <p>
                        Findings are consistent with early seropositive rheumatoid
                        arthritis.<span class="demo-caret"></span>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="demo-section is-visible" data-section="recs">
                    <h4>Recommendations</h4>
                    <p>
                        Initiate methotrexate with folic acid after baseline CBC, liver
                        enzymes, and chest radiograph; reassess disease activity in six
                        weeks.<span class="demo-caret"></span>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="demo-card demo-progress">
            <span class="demo-label">Progress</span>
            <ol class="demo-stages">
                <li class="demo-stage is-done" data-stage="standards">
                    <span class="demo-stage-icon"></span> Section standards
                </li>
                <li class="demo-stage is-done" data-stage="submit">
                    <span class="demo-stage-icon"></span> Draft submitted
                </li>
                <li class="demo-stage is-done" data-stage="hpi">
                    <span class="demo-stage-icon"></span> History of Present Illness
                </li>
                <li class="demo-stage is-done" data-stage="impression">
                    <span class="demo-stage-icon"></span> Impression
                </li>
                <li class="demo-stage is-done" data-stage="recs">
                    <span class="demo-stage-icon"></span> Recommendations
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
